data.description: Exceptional Florida living in an excellent location. This beautiful property features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a convenient carport sitting on an incredible lot surrounded by gorgeous trees and lovely foliage.  It’s everything you've been searching for, offering the perfect blend of style, comfort, and charm. When you step inside in your new home, you enter the bright and airy living room. Next, you will notice the kitchen has a lovely skylight and a door that leads you directly to your carport and laundry room. Your master bedroom features a nice walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom with a walk-in shower and dual vanities. Bedrooms 2 and 3 both have nice sized closets, which is another great bonus from this lovely home; storage space. Silestone Quartz countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms, as well as laminate and tile flooring throughout the home. New roof added in 2018 and the flat roof was replaced in 2020. The air ducts were replaced in 2019 and a brand new Air Conditioning was installed in 2022. There is a lot of space to really enjoy the outdoors here as well. You can add a garden, pergola, fire pit or just about anything to take advantage of this wonderful lot. Located in Fern Park/Casselberry, you'll enjoy easy access to local amenities, schools, and all of the parks the greater Orlando area has to offer.  Don't miss your chance to call this house your home. Schedule your showing today!
